    "pr_number": 7910,
    "issue_number": 6439,
    "issue_title": "BlockingPool num_idle_threads is wrongly double-increased when shutting down",
    "issue_body": "**Version**\r\nTokio v1.37.0\r\n\r\n**Description**\r\n`BlockingPool num_idle_threads` is doubly increased, when shutting down before the `condvar wait_timeout`.\r\n\r\nThe whole code is:\r\nhttps://github.com/tokio-rs/tokio/blob/9c337ca1a306be38e3474082be14bdef4bcb45b5/tokio/src/runtime/blocking/pool.rs#L519-L564\r\n\r\nWhen `BlockingPool` is shutting down, \r\nthe `num_idle_threads` will be increased at first in \r\nhttps://github.com/tokio-rs/tokio/blob/9c337ca1a306be38e3474082be14bdef4bcb45b5/tokio/src/runtime/blocking/pool.rs#L519\r\n\r\nand then it will doubly be increased in this\r\nhttps://github.com/tokio-rs/tokio/blob/9c337ca1a306be38e3474082be14bdef4bcb45b5/tokio/src/runtime/blocking/pool.rs#L564\r\n",
    "merged_at": "2026-02-17T07:19:51Z",
    "test_cmd": [
        "cargo",
        "test"
    ],
    "time_limit_seconds": 120,
    "output_token_budget": 50000,
